data.description: Beautiful, spacious, well maintained 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home in Noblesville. Great neighborhood for walking. This home is situated in a perfect location. Offering proximity to various amenities and conveniences. Main level is open concept, featuring a spacious kitchen with a pantry and island with countertop seating. The kitchen overlooks living area, a well-lit breakfast nook, and an outdoor semiprivate deck. Many upgrades, vinyl plank flooring, crown molding, 6" base boards on lower level, reverse osmosis water filter in kitchen. Upstairs features a desirable primary bedroom with a walk-in-closet and updated private bathroom. Three additional bedrooms are also on the upper level, and these each have their own walk-in-closet. There is also a 2nd floor loft. New roof, HVAC gas conversion installed in 2020, updated vent fans in upstairs bathrooms, new garage door springs.
